metadata.name: Anna #1/10
metadata.description:
Being a parent is so adventurous, we gather so many warm memories, sweetest moments, joy, sometimes it’s hard, sometimes sad. It is all so beautiful. 
But the biggest thing I am thankful for is that I had the opportunity to watch the purest thing on Earth - seeing my baby grow inside my wife’s body. 

Artist: Hrant Khachatryan

Camera: Fujifilm X-T20

Location: Armenia, Yerevan.

Date: 13.04.2020
